    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと、{user}\nなんでkanaについて来んの？",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ウザいんですけど？\n邪魔なんですけど？",
      "startTime": 8.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして嫌がらせ？\nkanaのSNS活動の妨害はやめてほしいんだけど？",
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "邪魔なんてしません\n俺に手伝えることがあればと思って",
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "これまでのいきさつはどうあれ\n今はkanaさんとスリクスのマネージャーですから",
      "startTime": 23.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "本気で言ってんの？\nだとしたら、マジでお人好し過ぎるんだけど",
      "startTime": 28.65,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "信用出来ませんか？",
      "startTime": 32.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、出来ない\nっていうか、kanaは他人のこと信用してないから",
      "startTime": 36.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "相手が{user}だから\n信用してないって訳じゃないよ",
      "startTime": 41.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、信用してなくても、仕事はちゃんとやるって\n問題は起こさないから。kana、大人だし",
      "startTime": 49.0081144422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしてそんな風に思うんですか？",
      "startTime": 53.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、そんなこと、今はどうでもいいじゃん\nそれより、ついて来るんだったら全力で協力しなよ？",
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、あのお店を背景にkanaを撮る！\n位置はそのまま、逆光にならないように！",
      "startTime": 70.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "今、手が下がった！\nそれだと顔の角度が変わっちゃうじゃん",
      "startTime": 76.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんの指定、細か過ぎです……",
      "startTime": 79.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "kanaを手伝いたいって言うなら\nこれくらいで音を上げないでくんない？",
      "startTime": 84.5333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7099.9999999000065,
          "startTime": 91.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かりましたよ。撮りますからね？　はい、チーズ",
      "startTime": 87.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "昭和かよ、古過ぎて逆にウケる",
      "startTime": 92.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4633.3333334000035,
          "startTime": 96.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 98.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7133.3333334000035,
          "startTime": 99.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8202.777099599998,
          "startTime": 100.3361104329
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13706.472269800002,
          "startTime": 105.8398056031
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、もっと撮って。あと100枚くらいね\nその中で一番マシなのアップするから",
      "startTime": 100.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "が、頑張ります……",
      "startTime": 103.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6899.999999999992,
          "startTime": 110.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10433.3333333,
          "startTime": 114.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "これ、顔の角度悪い。ボツ\nこれ、少し暗い。ボツ",
      "startTime": 112.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "これは……！？\nkana、半目じゃん。速攻ボツ",
      "startTime": 117.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "こんだけ沢山撮って、一枚もいいのがないじゃん\n{user}、下手過ぎじゃない？",
      "startTime": 125.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんのこだわりが凄過ぎるんですよ……\nSNSの写真一枚に、ここまでしなくても",
      "startTime": 131.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるのかなー、このポンコツマネージャーは\nkanaのSNSは、遊びでやってるんじゃないの",
      "startTime": 141.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "何万、何十万のファンが見てるわけ\n半端な画像なんて投稿出来ないでしょ？",
      "startTime": 148.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど……分かりました",
      "startTime": 152.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、もう予約した時間だ。ほら行くよ",
      "startTime": 155.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "予約？　どこに？",
      "startTime": 160.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
